					<div id="test-content">
						<div class="accordion_child">
							<b>1.</b> Be creative with passwords &ndash; easy to remember but hard to guess!<br />
							<b>2.</b> Always be kind online!<br />
							<b>3.</b> Follow the Golden rule! Don't do anything online that you wouldn't do in real life.<br />
							<b>4.</b> If you are ever cyberbullied, STOP, BLOCK, and TELL a trusted adult. <br />
							<b>5.</b> Spelling counts! Check your spelling in everything you do online. <br />
						</div>
